descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone, this is the preset of my character called Cathrine.
She was a temptress at first but because of incompatibilities i changed her into a Nord.
The face really matches all bodyweights, so adjust as you like !

Required Mods:

SKSE: http://skse.silverlock.org/
SkyUI: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?
RaceMenu Mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624//?
ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?
(not really sure about this one) Ethereal Elven Overhaul: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?
ApachiiSkyHair: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
The Eyes of Beauty: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- : http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?

Instructions:

0. Download & install the above mods if you dont have those
1. Download and place at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
2. Open Skyrim using SKSE
3. Open the racemenu using the console (type: showracemenu) or use another custom racemenu
4. Select the Nord Race
5. Click the preset tab, press F9 open the load preset menu , select cathrine.
6. Click R, done!

Mods used for screenshots:

Tembtra Thief Armor UNP - CBBE: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59451/?
HighRes 4K CBBE Nude Female Re-Texture Mod: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2841/?
